:

*Vidio* sam ga pre neki dan. (I saw him the other day.)
On je *vidio* da je to nemoguće. (He saw that it was impossible.)
Neke stvari se mogu *videti* samo iznutra. (Some things can only be seen from the inside.)
Bilo je teško *videti* detalje. (It was hard to see the details.)
*Videvši* to, rešio sam da se vratim. (Having seen that, I decided to come back.)